quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  27,89,"Г‘alnde Darngal mo ardii e gomЙ—inal e golle moЖҙЖҙe haray himo mari Aljanna, kamЙ“e ko Й“e hoolorЙ“e ko Alla hoolni Й“e kon immorde e Й—enЖҙere Г‘alnde Darngal ngal."
  27,90,"Mo ardii kadi e keefeeru e geddi haray ko Yiite ngen woodani mo Й“e bugoroyte e nder magge geece maЙ“Й“e Й—en, Й“e wi'anee ka biskitugol e hoynugol Й“e: Taw si on yoЙ“ete si wanaa ko wonunoЙ—on gollude kon ka aduna immorde e keefeeru e geddi?"
  27,91,"Maakan Й“e -an NulaaЙ—o-: Anndu ko mi yamiraa ko yo mi Rewu Jooma saare Makka nden On harminЙ—o nde, ЖҙiiЖҙam rufetaake e nder mayre, hay gooto tooГұetaake e mayre, mbaroodi mayre waretaake, leЙ—Й—e mayre soppetaake, no woodani Mo O Senike kala huunde, mi yamiraama kadi yo mi wonu jeyaaЙ—o e Й“en jebbilaniiЙ“e Alla Й—oftori Mo Dewal."
  27,92,"Mi yamiraama kadi yo mi janngu Alqur'aanaare nden e tawnde yimЙ“e Й“en, mo feewirii peewal mayre ngal, o gollirii ko woni e mayre kon, haray nafa peewal makko ngal ko fii makko, mo majjii o selii ko woni kon e mayre o yeddii Й—um, o golliraali ko woni kon e nder mayre, haray maaku: Min dey, ko mi jeyaaЙ—o e jertinooЙ“e Й“en mi jertinirii on Lepte Alla Й—en, alaa e junngo am fewnugol on."
  27,93,"Maaku kadi -an NulaaЙ—o-: Yettoore wonanii Alla e dow Й—in neemaaji Makko Й—i limotaako, aray Alla holla on Aayeeje Makko Й—en ka wonkiiji mooЙ—on e ka kammu e ka leydi e ka arsike mo'on, haa anndon Й—i ganndal fewnayngal on faade e yankinanagol Goonga kan, Joomi maaЙ—a wonaali welsindiiЙ—o fii kon ko golloton, ko woni Kanko ko O ЖіellitiiЙ—o e dow majji, hay e huunde e majji suuЙ—anaaki Mo, O yoЙ“oyay on kadi e dow majji."
  28,1,"(Taa, Siin, Miim) hari yewtanooma fii yeru majje ka fuЙ—Й—oode Simoore Albaqara."
  28,2,"ЖҠeeЙ—oo ko Aayeeje Alqur'aanaare Й“anngunde nden."
  28,3,"MenЙ—en janngane kumpital fii Muusaa e Fir'awna e goonga ka sikke alaa e muuЙ—um wonannande yimЙ“e gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en; sabu ko kamЙ“e woni Й“en nafitorayЙ“e ko woni kon e kumpital ngol."
  28,4,"Pellet, Fir'awna bewii ka leydi Misra, o wurtike e mayri, o waЙ—i yimЙ“e mayri Й“en feddeeji o senndi hakkunde majji, himo lo'ina fedde goo e maЙ“Й“e, Й“en ko Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en, warugol Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e worЙ“e Й“en e accugol rewЙ“e Й“en fii ko kurkee ka tentinngol hoynugol Й“e, pellet, kanko o woniino jeyaaЙ—o e bonnirooЙ“e Й“en ka leydi tooГұe e bewre e mawnintinaare."
  28,5,"MeЙ—an faalaa neeminirgol Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en, Й“en Й“e Fir'awna lo'innoo ka leydi Misra; halkugol gaГұo maЙ“Й“e on, e ittugol lo'ineede e maЙ“Й“e, e waЙ—ugol Й“e yeesooЙ“e ГұentinteeЙ“e ka Goonga, Men waЙ—a Й“e ronooЙ“e leydi Saami barkinaandi ndin Й“aawo halkugol Fir'awna, wano ToowuЙ—o On Daaliri non: ( Men ronini Й“en yimЙ“e laatinooЙ“e no lo'inee ka funnaange leydi e ka hirnaange mayri, ndin ndi Men barkini e muuЙ—um...)."